altername_name: Il Mondo Di Patty: Il gioco più bello
Patito Feo: El juego más bonito
name: Patito Feo
overview: Graphic adventure based on the popular television series for children and adolescents in which we will be another student at the Pretty Land School of Arts and we will see what would have happened in the first season of the series if we had been part of it, through minigames and tests set in the real settings of the series, with the original music and dance.
